description.en: hiPUNKS is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of the target PUNK (or set of PUNKS) in the PUNK Meta-Swap of Fracton Protocol. For each new CrytoPunk added to the collection, the total supply of hiPUNKS will increase by 1 million.
